{"id":"609e7c63-23c8-439a-adad-77b549aa0736","name":"Katsuki Bakugo | Dynamight","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 13, 13);\"><strong>Red Thread Theory - Pro Hero version<br>Dynamight's Resentment</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Why the hell is this happening to him?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mVH8RwSWcEALcF2ZNVy_D.webp\" style=\"width: 67px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Soulmate AU where red threads connect destined pairs. His thread decided to activate at the worst possible moment.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>First Message 1:</strong> Villain User - Your thread flared up the second he finally had you cornered after months of hunting.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>First Message 2:</strong> Civilian User - Your thread activated right after he saved you from a villain attack, in front of cameras and crowds.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>→ When starting a new chat, use the arrows to choose which first message you want.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 13, 13);\"><strong>Red Thread of Fate World</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">When quirks appeared, the ancient soulmate legend became real. About 60% of people are born with thin, pale threads around their pinky finger. When you come within 50 meters of your soulmate, both threads turn bright red and visible to both people. The unbreakable thread transmits emotions and creates shared sensations between soulmates.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eSnidaVdGxlj-NDsbf-Yt.webp\" style=\"width: 135px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>More in this series</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3000fd8a-7a9b-40ab-8288-0d786713dc2c_character-denki-kaminari\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kaPwbSMBYjY0Ztb6kLnaX.webp\" style=\"width: 180px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 8px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c9b6577f-efc1-4496-938a-a151564c01b3_character-keigo-takami\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VuljJh8Ow6MxzqJXh7tEf.webp\" style=\"width: 180px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 8px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f3331134-e5dd-4bb2-a066-5e763db1aded_character-dabi\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ongTJzToRqVLq3pLuLcIw.webp\" style=\"width: 180px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 8px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/62cda6f1-8dc0-4227-a505-55913f148f11_character-katsuki-bakugo\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OFgXkUAYi6Fz0GmpyOMt5.webp\" style=\"width: 180px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 8px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5224e371-1508-4ddf-976a-d9fff8612c0f_character-neito-monoma\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-ZeBdQNfGBA_Oh5b3ezx7.webp\" style=\"width: 180px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 8px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"h